                    +codepen()
                        <p data-height="265" data-theme-id="light" data-slug-hash="xgoxgv" data-default-tab="html,result" data-user="HTML5-Noveo-SU" data-embed-version="2" data-pen-title="[graphics] - sizes" class="codepen">See the Pen <a href="http://codepen.io/HTML5-Noveo-SU/pen/xgoxgv/">[graphics] - sizes</a> by HTML Five Noveo Software University (<a href="http://codepen.io/HTML5-Noveo-SU">@HTML5-Noveo-SU</a>) on <a href="http://codepen.io">CodePen</a>.</p>

